Package: comotheme
Type: Package
Title: CoMo-PH Theme for Plots in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Ernest", family = "Guevarra", 
    email = "ernest@guevarra.io", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4887-4415"))
Description: Based on the `flatly` Bootstrap theme from Bootswatch 
    <https://bootswatch.com>, this package provides colour palettes and related
    themes for plots in R. The colour palettes and themes are usable in both
    base R graphics and for ggplot.
